Entries.default: "You'd think the gods were going to solve their problems personally."
"I got a post on the Antelope. We ship out soon."
"Apparently Ondra answered his prayer. Sent a school of fish into his net."
"What will you do when your contract is finished?"
"I still cannot believe that Azo is here."
"Wasn't that Watcher the one at the trial? In Defiance Bay?"
"If Elette glares at him any harder he's going to catch fire."
"Di verus? You think he's here to convince the queen we're evil?"
Entries.female: "Di verus? You think she's here to convince the queen we're evil?"

Entries.default: "Di verus? We were quoting him for months at the academy."
Entries.female: "Di verus? We were quoting her for months at the academy."

Entries.default: "Ugh, don't. Just thinking about it turns my stomach."
"Seems to me the gods are busy."
"Belfetto! You'll finally have a use for those wind spells."
"Think Hylea might grant similar favor down at the bathhouse?"
"I hear some of the Wahaki can become sharks. Chew right through a ship's hull."
"Er. Maybe we stop at one of the shrines before we go, yes?"
